{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"e102176561","title":"准备充分后再打欧震","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"cd238be3c7","index":0,"year":1947,"month":1,"day":19,"articleId":"e102176561"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji22","name":"毛泽东全集第22卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji22.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji22":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"670137494a","type":"paragraph","text":"准备充分后再打欧震”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"e102176561"},{"id":"2c64e0cc43","type":"paragraph","text":"（1947年1月19日）陈，乘、谭","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"e102176561"},{"id":"d677c15984","type":"paragraph","text":"前电要你们迅速准备打欧震，但欧震集团北进甚速，数日内即将占领陇海线。如果各部准备不及，不能好敌于立足未稳之时，则率性推识至两星期以后发起开击，以期准备充分，一举解决欧军大部至全部似较有利：仓卒去打，只能开灭一部，又要休整方能再战，不如准备充分再打为宜。二十六师进占向城、兰陵二十大后我军仍能于两日内攻齐，即是一证。如何，望你们按情的定","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"e102176561"},{"id":"08d94e629a","type":"paragraph","text":"军委","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"e102176561"},{"id":"46dddd498b","type":"paragraph","text":"子酷[1]这是毛泽东为中共中央军委起草的给山东野战军司令员兼政治委员陈毅、华中野战军司令员票裕和政治委员谭震林的电报。2]欧震，当时任国民党军整编第十九军军长。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"e102176561"}],"page":{"id":"0c008f7b2a","publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"e102176561","start":376,"end":376}}}},"__N_SSG":true}